    <constructs>RC+xi, Reasoning Forge, AEGIS, QuantumSpiderweb, Memory Cocoons, Adapter Training, All Experimental Benchmarks</constructs>
    <sections>
      <section id="3" label="Theoretical Foundation">RC+xi formalism: Eq. 1-3 (state evolution, tension, convergence), 6 axioms</section>
      <section id="4.2" label="Reasoning Forge">Mean-field consensus update: Eq. 4, 5-agent + 11-agent synchronization</section>
      <section id="4.3" label="QuantumSpiderweb">5D cognitive graph, propagation, entanglement, collapse operations</section>
      <section id="4.4" label="Memory Cocoons">CognitionCocooner, DreamReweaver, encrypted persistence</section>
      <section id="4.6" label="AEGIS">Ethical governance: Eq. 9, recursive anchor, kill-switch, audit trail</section>
      <section id="5" label="Adapter Training Lab">LoRA/QLoRA config, 8 adapters, CPU pipelines (Sec 5.3)</section>
      <section id="6" label="Formal Methods">Definitions 1-9, Theorem 1 (convergence), Table: theoretical antecedents</section>
      <section id="7" label="Experiments">Tables 4-8: adapter scores, convergence, emergence, cocoon meta-analysis, uniqueness</section>
    </sections>
    <equations>
      <eq id="1">A_{n+1} = f(A_n, s_n) + epsilon_n (recursive state evolution)</eq>
      <eq id="2">epsilon_n = ||A_{n+1} - A_n||^2 (epistemic tension)</eq>
      <eq id="3">lim epsilon_n = 0 implies A_n -> A* (convergence)</eq>
      <eq id="4">lim |x_i(t) - x_j(t)| -> 0 (consensus)</eq>
      <eq id="5">E = hbar * omega (Planck-orbital node interaction)</eq>
      <eq id="6">S = alpha * psi_1 * psi_2* (entanglement sync)</eq>
      <eq id="7">I(t) = kappa * [f_base + Delta_f * coherence(t) + beta*H(t)] (intent modulation)</eq>
      <eq id="8">integral |F(k)|^2 dk &lt; epsilon_threshold (cocoon stability)</eq>
      <eq id="9">M(t) = lambda*R(t-dt) + H(t) + gamma*Learn(t) + mu*Regret(t) (ethical anchor)</eq>
      <eq id="10">A_{n+1}^i = f(A_n^i, 1/N sum_j A_n^j) + epsilon_n^i (forge update)</eq>
      <eq id="11">Gamma = 1/N sum |cos(theta_i - theta_bar)| (phase coherence)</eq>
      <eq id="12">s_i = (psi, tau, chi, phi, lambda) in R^5 (state vector, Def 1)</eq>
      <eq id="13">E_i = ||s_i||^2 (node energy, Def 2)</eq>
      <eq id="14">xi_ij = ||s_i - s_j||^2 (pairwise tension, Def 3)</eq>
      <eq id="15-16">b_h = rho^h * b_0, beta_h = 0.3 * rho^h (belief propagation, Def 4)</eq>
      <eq id="17">|mu_h - mu_k| > delta_anomaly (anomaly rejection, Def 5)</eq>
      <eq id="18-19">S_ij = alpha*psi_i*(-psi_j), state blend (entanglement, Def 6)</eq>
      <eq id="20">theta_i = atan2(phi_i, psi_i) (phase angle, Def 7)</eq>
      <eq id="21">||s_i - c_k|| &lt;= r_max (attractor detection, Def 8)</eq>
      <eq id="22">sigma_i = (1 + E_spec)^-1, threshold 0.3 (glyph stability, Def 9)</eq>
      <eq id="23-24">xi_W &lt; xi_thresh AND decreasing trend (Theorem 1: convergence)</eq>
      <eq id="25">xi_ij^sem = 1 - cosine(v_i, v_j) (semantic tension)</eq>
      <eq id="26">Gamma^sem = 1/N sum cosine(v_i, c) (ensemble coherence)</eq>
      <eq id="27">P = xi_bar * C_synth (tension productivity)</eq>
      <eq id="28">delta_R = (xi_1 - xi_R) / xi_1 (debate convergence)</eq>
    </equations>
